high_descs: Turn right and walk into the kitchen and up to the counter just right of the stove
Open the top right cabinet above the counter and retrieve the vase
Turn right and walk over to the fridge
Put the vase into the fridge and close it
Turn left and walk over to the kitchen sink
Open the cabinet below the sink and remove the vase
Turn right and walk back over to the fridge
Put the vase in the fridge next to the other one
anns.task_desc: Put the vases into the fridge

high_descs: turn right and walk over to the end of the kitchen island, then turn right again and walk over to the sink, turn and face the left kitchen counter
grab a vase out of the cabinet above the kitchen counter on the right
turn around and walk to the end of the kitchen island, and turn left to face the fridge
put the vase inside of the fridge
turn left and walk to the end of the kitchen island, then turn right to face the kitchen sink
grab the vase out from underneath the kitchen sink
turn right and walk over to the fridge again
place the second vase inside the fridge
anns.task_desc: place two vases inside of the fridge

high_descs: Turn around, walk towards the sink then turn left and face the cabinets above the countertop.
Open the door and pick up the glass bottle in the cabinet.
Go to the right and face the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator and place the glass bottle inside.
Close the refrigerator and move to the left to face the sink.
Open the cabinet below the sink and remove the glass bottle.
Go to the right to face the refrigerator.
Place the glass jar inside of the refrigerator next to the other glass jar.
anns.task_desc: Place both glass jars inside of the refrigerator.
